<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262053>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Megatibicen dealbatus n. comb.: A, male and female habitus; B, male dorsum; C, male timbal cover; D, male operculum. E, female operculum; F, male lateral view of genitalia; G, male posterior view of genitalia; H, female lateral view of genitalia; I, female ventral view of genitalia. Scale bar: A, 2 cm; B – E, 5 mm; F – G, 2 mm; H – I, 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

